  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The creative pixel-mapping fixture from Solaris LED. 3 to 48 DMX channels per fixture, based on settings 1, 4, or 16 “pixel” groups per fixture, based on settings. Extremely compact 120 x 120 x 46 mm. Only 0.6 kg!\n•Great for low weight load-bearing structures and surfaces.\n•Approx. 11,000 NITS! Brighter than nearly all outdoor LED walls!\n•Moisture and dust resistant IP54 enclosure.\n•Ultra-high refresh rate – 38,400Hz! Great for high-speed photography and videography.\n•Single cable, simple power-data connections, daisy-chain or split – easily place a Mozart almost anywhere.\n•Easy remote addressing and mode switching via RDM.",
